            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading">Nouveau site internet</h2>
            <p>11/07/2024</p>
            <img src="{{ asset('images/news/news-1.png') }}" alt="">
